data.description: This fully renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home on a large lot leaves nothing to be desired. The home has been updated from the top down and features new flooring, drywall, spray foam insulation, new roof, new fence, new siding, new HVAC and ducting, new windows, new kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances, full renovated bathrooms, and granite countertops throughout. Conveniently located near downtown, highways, schools, and shopping.
